00:00:00.50>AFR982 ORIG LEGR
00:00:00.50>AFR982 DEST LHBP
#00:00:00.50>AFR982 ADDWPT NETUN,
00:00:00.50>AFR982 ADDWPT IDROX,
00:00:00.50>AFR982 ADDWPT MAKAG,
00:00:00.50>AFR982 ADDWPT VELIM,
00:00:00.50>AFR982 ADDWPT ATRUP,


