00:00:00.50>WZZ012 ORIG LEBB
00:00:00.50>WZZ012 DEST LIRN
#00:00:00.50>WZZ012 ADDWPT VALMA,
00:00:00.50>WZZ012 ADDWPT TORLI,
00:00:00.50>WZZ012 ADDWPT IDROX,
